# Revision history for PAGI-Tools

0.002000
  - The PAGI application toolkit (PAGI::Runner, PAGI::Middleware::*,
    PAGI::App::*, PAGI::Endpoint::*, PAGI::Request/Response/Context,
    PAGI::Test::*) split out of the PAGI distribution into its own
    distribution. Git history preserved from the original repository
    (https://github.com/jjn1056/pagi).
  - New PAGI::Tools module anchors the distribution.
  - For changes prior to 0.002000, see the Changes file of the PAGI
    distribution (versions up to 0.001023).
